<asp:Content ID="Content1" ContentPlaceHolderID="headContent" runat="server">
</asp:Content>
<asp:Content ID="Content2" ContentPlaceHolderID="MainContent" runat="server">
    <div>
        <span class="glyphicons glyphicons-temple-christianity-church mypage-glythicons"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="mypage-header text-center">
        <h4><b>Beliefs</b></h4>
    </div>
    <div class="jumbotron text-Left">

        <div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse1">We believe in God; Eternal and Almighty</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse1" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        We believe in God Who is the Eternal and Almighty Creator of all things. (Eph 3:9; Gen. 1:1).
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2">We believe God is One Being of three persons</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse2" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        We believe God is One Being of three persons, the Father, the Son, and the Holy Spirit. (1Peter 1:2).
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse3">We believe in the deity of Jesus Christ</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse3" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        We believe in Jesus Christ, in His being the Son of God, in His virgin birth, in His Deity, and in His resurrection and ascension. (John 3:16; Heb. 1:8; Acts. 1:9; Mat. 28:58).
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse4">We believe in the Holy Spirit, the Third Person of the Triune God</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse4" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        We believe in the Holy Spirit, that He is the Third Person of the Triune God and the Divine Spirit through whom the Father and Son work.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse5">We believe in the New Birth</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse5" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        We believe in the New Birth, that, when a sinner comes to God and repents of his sins and receives forgiveness, that he is made a new creation in Christ Jesus. (2 Cor. 5:17; 1Peter 1:23; John 3:3)
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse6">We believe in the Baptism of the Holy Spirit</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse6" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        We believe in the Baptism of the Holy Spirit, that it is an endowment of power from on high upon the clean, sanctified life and that it is witnessed to in every case by speaking in tongues as the Spirit gives utterance. (Lu. 24:49; Mat. 3:11; John 7:38, 39; Acts 2:4; Mark 16:17, 18).
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse7">We believe in Sanctification</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse7" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        "that it is the cleansing of the heart from inbred sin, the changing of the carnal nature to the divine nature, and that it is wrought by the application of the blood of Jesus Christ through faith and consecration to God and that this experience of grace is subsequent to the new birth. (John 17:15-17; 1 Thes. 4:3; Heb. 2:11; 1 Peter 1:6; Eph. 1:6; 5:25-27; 2 Peter 1:4)."
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse8">We believe in the Bible Signs following believers</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse8" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        We believe in the Bible Signs following believers. (Mark 16:17; 1 Cor. 14:26).
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse9">We believe in Water Baptism by immersion</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse9" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        We believe in Water Baptism by immersion, in the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Ghost. (Matt. 28:19; Acts. 8:28,29).
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
             <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse10">We believe in the Divine Church</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse10" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        We believe in the Divine Church, built by Jesus Christ, that it embraces and includes everyone who is born into the household of faith. (Mat. 16:18; John 3:3; 1 Cor. 12:27; Eph. 2: 19-22).
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse11">We believe in the Holy Communion</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse11" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        We believe in the Holy Communion. (1 Cor. 11:23; Luke 22:17-20).
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse12">We believe in an eternal heaven and an eternal hell</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse12" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        We believe in an eternal heaven and an eternal hell, that the righteous will live eternally in heaven and the wicked will be eternally punished in the lake that burns with fire and brimstone. (Mat. 25:31-46; Rev. 14:10; Luke 16:24; Matt. 9:43, 44).
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse13">We believe in the Second Coming of Jesus Christ</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse13" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        We believe in the Second Coming of Jesus Christ, that it will be visible and literal as His going away. (Acts 1:9-11; John 14:3); that He will first come in the clouds to catch away His waiting Bride. (Mat. 24:40-44; 1 Thes. 4:15-17); and, immediately after the Tribulation to execute judgment upon the ungodly. (Matt. 24:29-31; 2 Thes 1:7-10; Jude 14-16; Zech. 14:3,4)
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</asp:Content>
